name: Bmi calculator javafx
body:
### Welcome to BMI Calculator
This application will ask your weight and height and calculate the BMI of the person and provides the details to verify that whether person is overweight, underweight, normal or obese 



### Authors and Contributors
Abhinav Tyagi (Master of Computer Information Systems @ Florida Tech)
